    "created_at": "2015-10-11T09:14:28Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-10-11T09:14:28Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "After testing the branch, here is my feeling:\n\nThe mousewheel should let zooming out much farer (currently, it only zooms out by 0.5) while it's possible to zoom in closer than 4.0. Imo, there is more interest in zooming out than zooming closer than 2:1.\n\nThe point of zooming out is to be able to view a large part of the battlefield. 0.5 is not enough. It currently doesn't feel like SupremeCommander.\n\nAlso, I noticed some graphic glitches sometimes:\n![screenshot001](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1732773/10415866/4edae7a4-6ffd-11e5-9e63-22a2361b9718.png)\n"
  },
